 <section xml:id="sec-switching-wicked">
  <title>Switching from <command>wicked</command> to NetworkManager</title>
  <para>
    To switch from <command>wicked</command> to the NetworkManager, follow the steps:
  </para>
  <procedure>
    <title>Disabling <command>wicked</command> and enabling NetworkManager</title>
    <step>
      <para>
        Disable the <literal>wicked</literal> service:
      </para>
      <screen>&prompt.root;systemctl disable wicked</screen>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>configure the NetworkManager as described in </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Enable the NetworkManager service:
      </para>
      <screen>&prompt.root;systemctl enable NetworkManager</screen>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Reboot your system.
      </para>
    </step>
  </procedure>
 </section>

